# VoidStack Portfolio - Environment Variables

# Backend API URL (only needed for production deployment)
# For Render.com: Set this to your backend service URL
# Example: VITE_API_URL=https://voidstack-api.onrender.com/api
VITE_API_URL=
# VoidStack Portfolio - Environment Variables
# In development, this is proxied automatically via vite.config.ts if blank.
# In production, set this to your backend service URL (e.g. on Render/Vercel)
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api
